<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Sovereign Capital | Pricing</title>
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="Review Sovereign Capital pricing across one-time acquisitions and recurring monthly plans, including debt systems, education, SaaS intelligence, memberships, and AI leverage."
    />
    <meta name="theme-color" content="#0A0A0A" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./assets/styles.css" />
    <script src="./assets/tailwind-theme.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  </head>
  <body class="bg-obsidian text-white antialiased">
    <div data-site-nav></div>

    <main class="site-shell pb-24 pt-32 sm:pt-36">
      <section class="relative px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="hero-orb red left-[10%] top-20 h-56 w-56" data-parallax data-speed="0.09"></div>
        <div class="hero-orb gold right-[8%] top-10 h-80 w-80" data-parallax data-speed="-0.07"></div>

        <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl">
          <div class="grid gap-10 lg:grid-cols-[1.02fr,0.98fr] lg:items-end">
            <div class="reveal max-w-4xl">
              <span class="section-kicker">Pricing Architecture</span>
              <h1 class="mt-8 font-display text-6xl leading-[0.92] text-white sm:text-7xl lg:text-[5.75rem]">
                Choose the access layer that matches your pace.
              </h1>
              <p class="mt-8 max-w-2xl text-base leading-8 text-zinc-300 sm:text-lg">
                Clean pricing. Premium experiences. One-time acquisitions for immediate leverage, and monthly plans for ongoing intelligence, community, and software.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="reveal premium-card rounded-[2rem] p-7 sm:p-8">
              <div class="card-shine"></div>
              <div class="relative z-10">
                <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.32em] text-zinc-500">Pricing note</p>
                <p class="mt-5 text-3xl text-white">All pricing is shown in USD. Digital Nation Citizenship is billed annually at $497/yr.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="reveal mt-12 flex flex-col gap-6 lg:flex-row lg:items-center lg:justify-between">
            <div class="price-toggle">
              <button type="button" class="active" data-plan-scope="one-time">One-Time</button>
              <button type="button" data-plan-scope="monthly">Monthly</button>
            </div>
            <p class="max-w-2xl text-sm leading-7 text-zinc-400" data-pricing-summary>
              <span class="text-white">One-Time Access:</span> Immediate acquisitions, flagship courses, and annual citizenship access.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="mt-16 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl">
          <div class="grid gap-6 lg:grid-cols-3" data-pricing-grid></div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="mt-24 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-7xl gap-6 lg:grid-cols-[0.95fr,1.05fr]">
          <div class="premium-card reveal rounded-[2rem] p-8 sm:p-10">
            <div class="card-shine"></div>
            <div class="relative z-10">
              <span class="section-kicker">Buying Logic</span>
              <h2 class="mt-6 font-display text-5xl text-white">Start with what removes friction. Add what compounds power.</h2>
              <p class="mt-6 text-base leading-8 text-zinc-300">
                The pricing architecture is designed to be intuitive: immediate tactical purchases up front, recurring intelligence and leverage once the operating system is in motion.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2">
            <div class="reveal rounded-[2rem] border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.03] p-7">
              <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-zinc-500">Lowest entry</p>
              <p class="mt-4 text-4xl text-white">$9</p>
              <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-7 text-zinc-300">Debt Destroyer Toolkit opens the ecosystem with immediate tactical clarity.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="reveal rounded-[2rem] border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.03] p-7">
              <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-zinc-500">Core monthly tier</p>
              <p class="mt-4 text-4xl text-white">$49/mo</p>
              <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-7 text-zinc-300">SaaS Premium, Monthly Insights Reports, and Vault Membership sit at the center of the recurring stack.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="reveal rounded-[2rem] border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.03] p-7">
              <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-zinc-500">Highest recurring tier</p>
              <p class="mt-4 text-4xl text-white">$149/mo</p>
              <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-7 text-zinc-300">Ultimate SaaS Bundle consolidates the entire SaaS intelligence environment.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="reveal rounded-[2rem] border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.03] p-7">
              <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-zinc-500">Private access tier</p>
              <p class="mt-4 text-4xl text-white">$497/yr</p>
              <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-7 text-zinc-300">Digital Nation Citizenship unlocks annual access to the deeper private ecosystem.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>

    <div data-site-footer></div>

    <div id="product-modal" class="modal" aria-hidden="true">
      <div class="modal-backdrop" data-modal-backdrop></div>
      <div class="modal-panel relative p-8 sm:p-10">
        <button
          type="button"
          class="absolute right-5 top-5 inline-flex h-11 w-11 items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] text-white"
          data-modal-close
          aria-label="Close modal"
        >
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.8" d="M6 18 18 6M6 6l12 12" />
          </svg>
        </button>
        <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.34em] text-zinc-500" data-modal-eyebrow>Product</p>
        <div class="mt-5 flex flex-col gap-4 sm:flex-row sm:items-end sm:justify-between">
          <h3 class="font-display text-4xl text-white sm:text-5xl" data-modal-title>Sovereign Product</h3>
          <p class="font-tech text-3xl text-gold" data-modal-price>$0</p>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-6 max-w-3xl text-base leading-8 text-zinc-300" data-modal-body></p>
        <div class="mt-8 grid gap-3" data-modal-list></div>
        <div class="mt-10 flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row">
          <a href="#" class="btn-primary">Buy Now</a>
          <button type="button" class="btn-secondary" data-modal-close>Close</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <script src="./assets/app.js" defer></script>
  </body>
</html>
